KeysToEntries.1_12_1-03:
This course is fun—
Lots of ups and downs, real tricky.
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-04:
Driving here…
makes you realize you’ve got to improve.
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-05:
Damn it!
Quit riding me like that!
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-08: (His line’s flawless… I can’t look away…)
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-10: Hmm…? Feels like someone’s on my tail…
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-11: Omiya… check the plate on the S14 up front…
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-12: Yeah… I see it… it’s a Gunma plate…
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-14:
Doesn’t matter either way…
Let’s take ’em out first.
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-16: They’re right on me…!! These punks… no way!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-17:
Shit…!!
They blew past me all at once!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-18: What the hell… that was too easy…
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-22:
Not bad at all…
caught me the second I eased up…
KeysToEntries.1_12_1-23: Damn… that was a cheap shot.
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-01: Man, this just doesn’t sit right…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-02: They call this a four-layer blockade…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-03:
Feels like since we’re first,
we’re not allowed to win…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-04:
Plenty of horsepower…
and damn smooth in the fast sections.
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-06:
Even on this rough road,
he’s not wasting any wheel spin.
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-07: Tch tch… that car’s built damn well…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-09: Still… it feels a little off…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-10: What the hell…? Feels like something’s off…!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-11: No doubt, you’ve got driving skills…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-12:
Still doesn’t mean
you’re any better than me…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-13: So losing isn’t an option for me…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-15: Don’t forget, it’s a damn Evo!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-16: Don’t think I’m dumb… I’ve already read you.
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-17: He’ll make his move… but when, where…!?
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-19: Damn, I slipped… didn’t expect that…!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-21:
No… I can catch him…
I’ll close the gap… I swear…
KeysToEntries.1_12_2-22: I need to close that gap!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-01: I’ll give the best run I’ve ever had…
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-03:
Kobayakawa tried to watch by
following from behind…
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-04: But there’s a catch to that.
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-05: It proves he hasn’t found his own pace…
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-06: That’s why I’m going to take the lead!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-07:
Empty road, my pace…
because I’m here to win!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-09:
No mirror needed, I feel it…!!
He’s right on me!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-10:
To push it that far…!!
It’s practically a miracle…!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-11: At this point, there's no tricks left…
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-13:
“This space is mine…
let’s see if you can keep up!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-15:
Did the spoiler clip…!? 
My balance is screwed…!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-16:
No excuses…
I’ll push my limits with sheer will…!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_3-18: Guess… it just wasn’t my day…
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-02:
I saw Takumi’s moves
during that fake Project D showdown…
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-03:
I’ll pull off the drift I picked up
I picked up riding shotgun!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-04: Well, well… that should be fun.
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-06: (Heh… looks like you’re half decent after all…)
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-09:
Push it harder!
That car’s begging for more!
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-10: Ugh, I… I can’t go any more…
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-11: Don’t slack— I’m upping the pace!
KeysToEntries.1_12_4-18: Tch… guess I still can’t catch you…
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-01: Alright! Let’s fire up for the second run!
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-03:
(I knew Wataru was passionate…
but not this much…)
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-07: Well… you did better than I thought.
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-09: Oh-ho… there’s a lively one here…
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-10: But still… not enough to make me go all out…
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-11: That white & black 86… is it Fujiwara…?
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-12: No, Takumi went to the beach with Mika today…
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-13: Then… who the hell is this…?
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-14: Don’t tell me… Takumi’s old man…!?
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-15: Well... guess I’ll have a little fun…
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-16:
(Still, once it clicks…
this car feels amazing…)
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-17: (Way better balanced than I ever imagined…)
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-18:
(To tune a suspension this good
in such a short time…)
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-20: Damn it… he vanished just like that…!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-21:
Even you can’t take him…
What kind of driving is that…?
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-22:
Interesting… so there’s still more…
the world’s bigger than I thought…!!
KeysToEntries.1_12_5-23: (Uh… feels like they’ve forgotten about me…)
